<p local-id=3D"af8da8c04e65"><strong>MMM L2: </strong>(Pending PS Team enga=
gement)</p>
<p local-id=3D"7402fb70fdce">Harish has reached out to all Japan applicatio=
n owners; Ingenium data has been collected. Remaining Japan Gold app update=
s will be planned after <strong>PS Team</strong>&nbsp;members are assigned.=
&nbsp; Debamalya owns checklist / project-plan distribution back to the wor=
king group.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"1d6c7428e08b">
<li local-id=3D"0a48705fc6a5">
